<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko" dir="ltr">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>JAM : 제주대 활동관리 사이트 > 팀원모집</title>
  </head>
  <style>
    body{
      background-color:aliceblue;
    }
    .header {position: absolute; font-size : 2em; font-weight: bolder; padding: 20px; margin:20px; }
    .tab > a:first-child {position: absolute; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 550; border:3px solid black; padding:7px; left:1300px; top: 62px; border-radius: 10px;}
    .tab > a:nth-child(2) {position: absolute; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 550; border:3px solid black; padding:7px; left:1430px; top: 62px; border-radius: 10px;}
    .tab > a:nth-child(3) {position: absolute; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 550; border:3px solid black; padding:7px; left:1570px; top: 62px; border-radius: 10px;}
    .line {position: absolute; width: 97%; left: 32px; top: 110px; border-bottom: 1px solid black;}
    .blank {height: 120px;}
    
